"codes of land cover classes. A **Macroclass** is a group of ROIs having "
"different Class ID, which is useful when one needs to classify materials "
"that have different spectral signatures in the same land cover class. For "
"instance, one can identify grass (e.g. ``ID class = 1`` and ``Macroclass ID "
"= 1`` ) and trees (e.g. ``ID class = 2`` and ``Macroclass ID = 1`` ) as "
